{{trivia}}
==Trivia==
* Taylor-Compton's nicknames are Scoutie and Skully.
* Taylor-Compton was originally cast as one of the 'six chicks' in ''[[13 Going On 30]]''. Her role, as well as four of the other six chicks, were recast for appearing too old.  The original young Jenna and Matt were also recast.
* In the episode "White Balance " of ''[[Without a Trace]]'', two teenagers go missing at the same time - a boy and a girl. Taylor-Compton played the girl, Emily Grant.<ref name="scouttrace2">[http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0789757/ "Without a Trace" White Balance]  Source: [[Internet Movie Database]]</ref>

